description: We developed a software for extraction of protein decay rate constants from heavy water labeling followed by LC-MS experiments. We illustrate the program on application to normal diet and western diet fed LDLR-/- mice. We demonstrate that proteins subunits of 40S ribosomal complex have reduced stability in western diet fet mice.

title: D2Ome - rate constant estimation from heavy water metabolic labeling and LC-MS
